{"tid":2176800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除左著黑衫，仲有野可以做","createTime":"2020-08-27T09:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T15:21:03.000Z","uid":241507,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0439d3114738a57dc4631f2aba23ad1888a3fa3","tid":2176800,"uid":241507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"今日咁嬲你同我著件衫就算?<br />\n呢個聯署吹左雞咁耐都係5萬未夠呀!!<br />\n<br />\n聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=b7a8935e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a><br />\n<br />\n對家依靠係咁打壓，因為個疫情我地無得出黎<br />\n唔可以俾佢地回氣，各方面要佢地承受更多痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nif we burn, CCP burn with us<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e166448c59cc69ce92222294781e194f582b98b6","tid":2176800,"uid":241507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"we chat 被禁對你工作無影響，因為個個會轉去whatsapp, LINE, email<br />\n<br />\n但對中共黎講，佢地可以用既武器又少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60085eddadb73e68c41d05bdda12d02a9459bc29","tid":2176800,"uid":241507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"抖音呢d<br />\n更加係中共用黎洗腦加資訊控制既野<br />\n<br />\n你想玩既就等其他新app, 或者佢海外版俾人收購左先玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但聯署就同我簽左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f71c2bf2c8ab386ab1b79976ff40f18d545cf1f","tid":2176800,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10